title: We Send Lunchbox Off to The Arkansas Diamond Mine + The Best and Safest Songs to Drive To + We Talk Gary Levox and play “Hump It Or Dump It?” with His New Song
itunes:title: We Send Lunchbox Off to The Arkansas Diamond Mine + The Best and Safest Songs to Drive To + We Talk Gary Levox and play “Hump It Or Dump It?” with His New Song
description:
Happy Mon-yay! Today is the day that we send Lunchbox to mine for Diamonds in Arkansas. It may be the last day we see him…because he says if he finds a diamond worth at least 1 million dollars, he’s quitting the show! Bobby has a list of the best songs to drive to and the safest songs to drive to. Bobby calls Gary Levox to talk about his new song “Working On Sunday” from an upcoming solo album.
